    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolute showstopper! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and feeling exactly like it just arrived from the factory. From the flawless paint to the immaculate interior, every inch of this car has been meticulously preserved for the next owner to enjoy a like-new driving experience.",
